Download the selenium standalone server jar
run command to make your system as hub
	-java -jar selenium-server-standalone-3.141.59.jar -role hub
Nodes should register at this hub ip address (you'll get in step 3 ip)

login to machine where node is being registered
	- Download the selenium standalone server jar in node machine as well
	- run command to make your system as node and connect with hub
		- java -Dwebdriver.chrome.driver="C:\\chromedriver.exe" -jar 
		  selenium-server-standalone-3.141.59.jar -role webdriver -hub 
		  ipaddress -port 5556
		Note: java should be configured in node system with system variable setup
		Note: ChromeDriver.exe should be placed 

	